show.description: When an oil company accidentally frees a massive prehistoric shark from its icy tomb, chaos erupts in the open waters. Stranded on a remote island, a group of ruthless thieves and unsuspecting college students must fight to survive as the ancient predator stalks them. With no escape and the beast closing in, they must outsmart the ultimate killing machine before becoming its next meal.
